  "title": "Enterprise Risk Management - Up to S$8k",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Ensure alignment with group compliance and risk frameworks.</li><li>Advise business units on compliance issues, regulatory requirements, and risk mitigation strategies.</li><li>Maintain and execute the annual compliance plan, ensuring timely completion of activities.</li><li>Exercise oversight on third party and outsourcing risk, ensuring alignment with internal frameworks, policies, and procedures.</li><li>Support and coordinate independent assurance reviews of outsourced activities performed by intragroup entities, ensuring compliance with regulatory and internal standards.</li><li>Review and reassess the scope of work in outsourcing arrangements to ensure robust risk and compliance oversight, and define, monitor, and report on Key Risk Indicators (KRIs) related to outsourcing and third-party risk, enabling proactive risk management and timely escalation of emerging issues.</li><li>Oversee and provide independent challenge and assurance on technology, cyber and data risks from second line perspective.</li><li>Supporting and advise compliance with regulatory requirements on technology risk management and cyber resilience in line with regulatory expectations.</li><li>Monitor and report on IT/data risk issues, incidents, and remediation status to governance forums.</li><li>Conduct risk-based reviews to validate control design and effectiveness. Perform risk and control self-assessments (RCSA) and control testing to evaluate effectiveness.</li><li>Support projects, reviews, and initiatives as directed by the Head of Risk and Compliance.</li></ul><p><br /><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Experience in regulated financial institutions by MAS, with strong regulatory knowledge and risk management expertise.</li><li>Excellent communicator, ability to translate regulatory requirements and communicating risk issues clearly to the business.</li><li>Experience on Technology, Cyber and Data risk</li></ul><p><br /><br />Kindly apply online or send your application to andylee@talentedge.com.sg</p><p>EA: 15C7572</p>",
